	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, there IS "fear kiting"...<br>Ok, so it's not exactly a true form of kiting, but once it sticks on the bad guys you can bash the mobs from behind until they regain their wits about themselves. <br>Simply done, you "Instill Doubt" them until it works, then just chase after it while punching/kicking/beating on it for as long as it lasts.<br><br>--Pusbag Infection<br>&nbsp;<br>Emperor and Shamanic High Priest of the Trolls<br>"Worship Innoruuk, you worthless cattle!"<br></td></tr>
